These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
City: liverpool, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| City   | san-francisco | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: bird, dog
1. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Pet   | bird | dog |

 #################################

 
